                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4">
                    <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-cutlery" aria-hidden="true"></i></h2>
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                        Enim rem odit deleniti. Magnam, illo alias, voluptatem 
                        tenetur minus quibusdam placeat fugit beatae ea, distinctio
                        blanditiis temporibus debitis consequatur exercitationem voluptate.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4">
                    <h2 class="text-center"><i class="fa fa-glass" aria-hidden="true"></i></h2>
                    <p class="text-justify">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                        Enim rem odit deleniti. Magnam, illo alias, voluptatem 
                        tenetur minus quibusdam placeat fugit beatae ea, distinctio
